casebody.data:
MOTION DOCKET

96-1269. AL Post 763 v. Ohio Liquor Control Comm.

Greene App. No. 95CA78. Sua sponte, cause consolidated for purposes of briefing and oral argument with 96-1572, 96-1575, and 96-2797, infra, with 96-2797 designated the lead ease.

Douglas, J., would dismiss the cause as having been improvidently allowed. Resnick, J., dissents to the court’s sua sponte order.
